00:28:30,744 --> 00:28:32,144
Who is this guy?
Captain Video?

439
00:28:32,237 --> 00:28:35,837
No, he's the best numbers-cruncher
in the free world.

440
00:28:37,177 --> 00:28:39,621
I'll be heading back to New York
in about 10 minutes,

441
00:28:39,622 --> 00:28:41,196
but Syd's going to stick around
for a couple of days...

442
00:28:41,197 --> 00:28:42,808
...and make sure
everything's on line.

443
00:28:42,809 --> 00:28:45,069
I thought you were going
to be in charge.

444
00:28:45,345 --> 00:28:47,645
I am, Mrs. Furman.
I'm in overall charge.

445
00:28:47,751 --> 00:28:50,003
Fortunately, Syd has consented
to make sure...

446
00:28:50,004 --> 00:28:52,851
...I don't screw up on
any of those details.

